44
00:03:44,594 --> 00:03:45,994
Petugas Chiba!

45
00:03:45,994 --> 00:03:47,794
Kau sudah menemukan seseorang?

46
00:03:47,794 --> 00:03:49,294
Tidak, belum.

47
00:03:49,294 --> 00:03:52,594
