164
00:09:34,694 --> 00:09:36,994
Saat dia jatuh dari atas,

165
00:09:36,994 --> 00:09:40,394
Bukankah Ny. Hirukawa berada di dalam mobil di tempat parkir

166
00:09:40,394 --> 00:09:43,094
bersama dengan kita berdua?

167
00:09:43,094 --> 00:09:44,494
Itu benar.

168
00:09:44,494 --> 00:09:46,294
Jadi, katakan,

169
00:09:46,294 --> 00:09:49,694
